"destra della linea temporale per chiudere il buco."

#: ../../user_interface/menu/timeline_menu.rst:215
msgid "Timeline Zone extracted from the Timeline"
msgstr "La zona della linea temporale estratta dalla linea temporale"

#: ../../user_interface/menu/timeline_menu.rst:217
msgid ""
"Pressing :kbd:`Z` or selecting :menuselection:`Menu --> Timeline --> Removal "
"--> Lift Timeline Zone` will cut the clips where the Timeline Zone starts "
